  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><style>[data-colorid=cy951cm7cd]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=cy951cm7cd]{color:#4c9fc2}[data-colorid=ht9231dmgy]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ht9231dmgy]{color:#4c9fc2}</style>Working with UDIMs in Blender is very straightforward.<br /><br />If your textures use the Mari UDIM style and the filename is:&nbsp;<strong>Diffuse.1001.tex</strong>, you need to set the <span data-colorid=\"ht9231dmgy\">Atlas Style</span> to UDIM (Mari) and in the filename parameter, use&nbsp;<strong>Diffuse.&lt;UDIM&gt;.tex&nbsp;</strong>for the textures to load into their correct UDIMs.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br />Note : &lt;UDIM&gt; can be in either UPPER or lowercase &lt;udim&gt;</p><p><br /><br /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638640/RenderMan_Blender_UDIMS.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432706673&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638640/RenderMan_Blender_UDIMS.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432706673&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638654\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_UDIMS.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638640\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3cdcf2db-74ec-49a5-a523-dd230c93b196\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><br /><br /><br /></p><p>A Mari UDIM example for the first UV tile would be&nbsp;<span data-colorid=\"cy951cm7cd\">Diffuse.1001.tex</span>&nbsp;where &quot;1001&quot; replaces &lt;UDIM&gt; in the texture filename.&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"fixed-table wrapped confluenceTable\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 69.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 162.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 205.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 180.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 168.0px;\" /></colgroup><thead><tr><th colspan=\"1\" class=\"confluenceTh\"><p>Value</p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p>Filename</p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p>Atlas Style</p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p>Use in path</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" class=\"confluenceTh\"><p>Alternative</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" class=\"confluenceTd\">0</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">Diffuse.1001.tex</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">UDIM (Mari)</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">Diffuse.&lt;UDIM&gt;.tex</td><td colspan=\"1\" class=\"confluenceTd\">Diffuse.&lt;udim&gt;.tex</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" class=\"confluenceTd\">1</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">Diffuse.U1_V1.tex</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">UV Tile Base-1 (Mudbox)</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">Diffuse.&lt;U&gt;_&lt;V&gt;.tex</td><td colspan=\"1\" class=\"confluenceTd\"><br /></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" class=\"confluenceTd\">2</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">Diffuse.u0_v0.tex</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">UV Tile Base-0 (Zbrush)</td><td class=\"confluenceTd\">Diffuse.&lt;u&gt;_&lt;v&gt;.tex</td><td colspan=\"1\" class=\"confluenceTd\"><br /></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><br /></p><p><br />Please refer to the full <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN24/pages/21759808/PxrTexture\" data-linked-resource-id=\"21759808\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrTexture </a>page for more information</p><p><br /></p>"
    }
